| **Security headers** | None set | Add `helmet()` |
| **CORS** | No policy | Add `cors()` with explicit origin |
| **Rate limiting** | None | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| **Body parsing** | Missing | Add `express.json()` with size limit |
| **Error handling** | No global handler | Add 404 + global error middleware |
| **Info leakage** | Stack traces exposed | Conditional error messages by `NODE_ENV` |
| **Fingerprinting** | `X-Powered-By` header | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
